=head1 DESCRIPTION

The filter to use to identify the subset of headers to inspect in a web
request.

You must specify exactly one setting: either C<All>,
C<IncludedHeaders>, or C<ExcludedHeaders>.

Example JSON: C<"MatchPattern": { "ExcludedHeaders": [ "KeyToExclude1",
"KeyToExclude2" ] }>

